Idambudziko rei rawaive naro kare?

0:00:13.020,0:00:15.800
Kurwadziwa kwakanyanya kwe ronda apa.

0:00:15.800,0:00:17.340
Saka, sezvamanga muchiparidza uko, ndati,

0:00:17.340,0:00:20.620
"Kana muri munhu wa Mwari, kana mukandibata uye kurwadziwa uku kukaenda, ndichaziva".

