Iwe haugone kuona chii?

0:00:28.200,0:00:29.680
Hapasisina kurwadziwa zvakare.

0:00:29.680,0:00:30.820
Marwadzo akaita sei?

0:00:30.820,0:00:31.920
Marwadzo echironda.

0:00:31.920,0:00:32.880
Kwemakore mangani?

0:00:32.880,0:00:34.420
Anopfuura makore 22.

0:00:34.420,0:00:36.040
Asi mushure mekukubata, chii chaitika?

