0:01:49.200,0:01:54.560
Zita rangu ndi Anoremekedzwa Jones Dangba. Ndinobva ku Abuja (Nigeria).

0:01:54.560,0:02:01.360
Takakumbirwa kuti tiuye kuzobvunzurudzwa, kuti chii chaitinetsa.

0:02:01.360,0:02:05.420
Sezvo ndakanga ndisina tsamba yavana chiremba yaitaura nezve chironda, handina kuzvitaura.

0:02:05.420,0:02:07.520
Saka pakati peusiku ndakamuka ndikati,

0:02:07.520,0:02:10.740
"Zvakanaka, Mwari, iyi ndiyo nhandare yerusununguko.

0:02:10.740,0:02:14.320
Kana uyu ari munhu wa Mwari uye ndinotenda ndiye nokuti ndizvo zvandiunza,

0:02:14.320,0:02:16.300
Ratidzai kuti iye munhu wa Mwari ".

0:02:16.300,0:02:19.700
Akauya shure kwangu akandibata. Ndakati, " Izvi ndizvo!"

0:02:19.700,0:02:22.700
Pakarepo ndakasimuka, akangotora ruoko rwake ndokurova ipo chaipo.

0:02:22.700,0:02:26.160
Haugoni kubata panzvimbo yacho nemunwe wako.

0:02:26.160,0:02:29.560
Akarova neruoko akapananga ndokubva ndawira pasi.

0:02:29.560,0:02:33.040
Akafamba akatenderera, akadzoka zvakare ndokundirova zvakare.

0:02:33.040,0:02:37.380
Sezvandakabata dumbu, hapana kana kurwadziwa zvako!

0:02:37.380,0:02:39.820
Ndakanga ndine dambudziko iri kwemakore 21 apfuura.

0:02:39.820,0:02:42.480
Baba vangu vakaenda kunova na Ishe.

0:02:42.480,0:02:44.620
Vakanga vaine dambudziko rimwe chete remaronda.

0:02:44.620,0:02:46.420
Amai vangu vane dambudziko re chironda.

0:02:46.420,0:02:47.940
Ndakanga ndine chironda chakafanana, uye ndakati,

0:02:47.940,0:02:50.860
"Mwari, chinhu ichi chinofanira kupera neni!"

0:02:50.860,0:02:54.860
Kunyangwe mwanasikana wangu muduku, uyo ari mubato reuto revechidiki, ane dambudziko iroro.

0:02:54.860,0:02:58.040
Ini ndakati, "Kwete, izvi ndizve dzinza; zvinofanira kupera neni nhasi!"

0:02:58.040,0:03:00.800
Asi zvakandishamisa ndezve kuti handina kuzvitaura

0:03:00.800,0:03:05.220
Uye ini ndakataura na Mwari chete mumoyo mangu, "Kana uyu ari munhu wa Mwari, ngaaone mhosva iyi".

0:03:05.220,0:03:07.660
Uye akandirova ipapo sekumira kwandakaita pano,

0:03:07.660,0:03:10.600
Handisati ndamboona rudzi rwekuporesa rwakadai kare, kubva pandakazvarwa.

0:03:10.600,0:03:14.040
Kusunguka zvachose! Mwari akaona chironda! Ndaporeswa!

0:03:14.040,0:03:17.680
Ameni. Ngatiisei maoko edu pamwe chete kuna Jesu Kristu!

0:03:17.680,0:03:21.020
Saka munoreva here kuti, changamire, kuti apo muporofita akanga achifamba-famba,

0:03:21.020,0:03:23.860
Nzvimbo chaiyo yaakakubatai

0:03:23.860,0:03:28.680
yakanga iri nzvimbo chaiyo yamaive ne chironda chakaipa kwemakore anopfuura makumi maviri.

