Hongu, chaizvoizvo makore 21.

0:03:30.700,0:03:33.080
Akaparova; Haana kungondibata chete.

0:03:33.080,0:03:37.040
Ndinoda kuvonga Mwari kuti ichi ndicho chipo changu chegore! rese

0:03:37.040,0:03:39.160
Ndayambuka zambuko rangu. Ameni.

0:03:39.160,0:03:40.400
Ndokutendai, Jesu Kristu.

0:03:40.400,0:03:43.200
Changamire, tiudzei - musati mauya ku SCOAN,

0:03:43.200,0:03:46.340
Marwadzo hwai amaiva nawo nekuda kwechironda ichi

0:03:46.340,0:03:48.780
Uye zvakakanganisa sei upenyu hwenyu?

0:03:48.780,0:03:51.580
Handaikwanisi kudya mhiripiri saizvozvo; Handaikwanisa.

0:03:51.580,0:03:56.700
Kana ndaidya chikafu cherumwe rudzi, ndaifanira kutenga mishonga ndozodya.

0:03:56.700,0:03:59.600
Vanondiziva mune chimwe chitoro chinotengesa mishonga chiri shure kweimba yangu.

0:03:59.600,0:04:03.180
Ndaigara ndichiti, "Ndipe chero chinhu chinorwisa ronda".

0:04:03.180,0:04:06.540
Apo vaindiona, muzvina mushonga aibva ati , "Chero chinopesana nemaronda!"

0:04:06.540,0:04:09.720
Saka pa vhiki rega rega, ndaipedza pakiti rimwe.

0:04:09.720,0:04:11.420
Pandaidya, ndaifanira kuutora.

0:04:11.420,0:04:14.880
Kana zvisina kudaro, ini ndaizofanira kunyunyuta. Handaizo rara zvakanaka.

0:04:14.880,0:04:17.940
Iye zvino, changamire, mungagone kungobata nzvimbo yamakanga muine dambudziko.

0:04:17.940,0:04:22.800
Iyi ndiyo nyaya iye zvino; Handisi kupanzwa

